dc_title_s: Portugallia et Algarbia quae olin Lusitania
dc_description_s: 1 map ; 38 x 50 cm.|Relief shown pictorially.|North oriented toward the right.|Decorative cartouche includes men with astronomical instruments and illustrations of Neptune and ships on the ocean. Two coats of arms are included.|This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637, and 1680.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
